name: LookAbove
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: look above
des:
Just because you cant see up far into the sky and beyond, doesn't mean you can't find out what is up there!

This skill looks deep into the skies about the major cities of the word, providing information on the number of planes, satellites and even meteorites that lie above the geographic centers (5 mile radius) of the worlds cities, as well as presenting you with a thought provoking picture of the universe each day, showing whats above in a way you've never seen!

Please note that data is updated every 10 minutes, and upon asking for a city, it might take a few seconds to load as there is lots of data to crunch.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
